&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Subsidized health and dental insurance plans (PPO and HMO options)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Monthly commuting subsidy for use of public transit or carpooling&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
